Dawuniloda umculo wakho kokuthi Njengoba Unjalo ukuze ulalele kukhwalithi yethu ephezulu kakhulu ngenkathi ungaxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi. Buyekeza ikhwalithi yokudawuniloda kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.connect-exp: Indlela engcono kakhulu yokulalela kokuthi Njengoba Unjalo iwukusebenzisa Ukuxhuma ku-Spotify. Vele udlale ingoma, bese uthepha okuthi {0} ngezansi kwesikrini ukuze ukhethe idivayisi futhi ulawule umculo wakho ukusuka ngqo ohlelweni.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.bluetooth-d: Ukusebenzisa i-Bluetooth kuzothinta ukulalela kokuthi Njengoba unjalo

Amadivayisi amaningi e-Bluetooth akwazi ukudlala ikhwalithi yomculo engcono kunokuthi Okuphezulu Kakhulu, kodwa awawusekeli ngokugcwele umsindo wokuthi Njengoba unjalo. Okuthi Njengoba Unjalo kujatshulelwa kangcono ngezipikha zokuXhuma ku-Spotify kanye/noma amadivayisi anezintambo.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.opt-out-of-: Shintsha amasethingi akho ukuze ujabulele ukulalela okushelela kakhudlwana

Usukhubazé isici sekhwalithi esizilungisa sona Kumasethingi. Lokhu kusho ukuthi ungase uphazamiseke ekulaleleni kwakho uma une-bandwidth ebuthaka ye-inthanethi. Ungavula lesi sici kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.poor-bandwi: Kubonakala sengathi i-bandwidth yakho ye-inthanethi inenkinga yokusekela okuthi Njengoba unjalo njengamanje. Zama ukuhlola ukuxhuma kwakho noma ushintshele kunethiwekhi ehlukile.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.default-to-: Shintsha amasethingi akho ukuze usakaze ngokuthi Njengoba unjalo

Ayikho into ephoxa njengokweqa kwengoma. Yingakho sikwehlisa ngokuzenzakalelayo kusuka kokuthi Njengoba Unjalo ukuya kukhwalithi yomsindo ephansi uma une-bandwidth ebuthaka. Ungavala isici sekhwalithi esizilungisa sona kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.need-to-red: Dawuniloda kabusha izingoma zakho ukuze uzidlale kokuthi Njengoba unjalo

Izingoma ozidawunilodile okwamanje azikho kokuthi Njengoba unjalo. Uma ufuna ukuzilalela kokuthi Njengoba unjalo, uzodinga ukuzidawuniloda kabusha. Ungakhohlwa phela ukuthi amafayela ezingoma zokuthi Njengoba unjalo makhulu futhi angasebenzisa isitoreji esiningi kakhulu. Ungashintsha ikhwalithi yomsindo wamadawunilodi akho kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.lossless-un: Siyaxolisa, le threkhi ayitholakali kokuthi Njengoba unjalo okwamanje.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.update-sett: Shintsha amasethingi akho ekhwalithi yomsindo ukuze usakaze kokuthi Njengoba unjalo
Usethe Amasethingi akho ukuthi adlale umculo kokuphezulu noma okuphansi Kakhulu. Ukuze ushintshe lokhu, iya kokuthi Amasethingi bese ukhetha okuthi Njengoba Unjalo.
action-trigger.login-playlist: Ngena ngemvume ukuze wakhe futhi wabelane ngezinhla zokudlalayo.
web-player.your-library-x.unpin-confirma: Ukuhambisa lolu hlu lokudlalayo kuzosusa ukuphina kokuphambili Komtapo Wakho
Ukuhambisa le folda kuzosusa ukuphina kokuphambili Komtapo Wakho
web-player.social-connect.invitation.qr-: Mema abangane ukuze bajoyine i-Jam yakho
Kopisha futhi yabelana ngesixhumanisi nabangane bakho, noma ubacele ukuthi baskene ikhodi ye-QR.
web-player.puffin.reset-headphones.dialo: Lokhu kuzophinde kusethe kabusha izinga lakho lokwenza umsindo ube ovamile. Lawula izinga lokwenza kube okuvamile ngekhasi Kumasethingi.
web-player.puffin.error-troubleshooting: Uxolo, lokhu akutholakali. Zama ukuxhuma kabusha amahedifoni akho.
web-player.puffin.manual-selection.empty: Zama ukusesha futhi usebenzisa isipelingi esihlukile noma igama eliyinhloko.
web-player.puffin.upsell.lossless-listen: Lawula ukulalela kwakho okuthi Njengoba Unjalo
web-player.connect.nudge.dj-voice-unavai: Ku-beta, izwi lika-DJ alitholakali kulesi sipikha
